data.description: Don't hesitate to schedule a tour to be 1st in backup position. This home is going to be a steal for someone. No worries turn key home ready for it's new home lovers. Utitlities have all been updated in the last few years including water heater, ac and furnace. Garage is insulated for a cozy workspace or keeping your cars ready to roll all winter without having to scrape your windows. Dog doors to backyard are ready to welcome your four legged family memebers to their new paradise and fully fenced giant backyard. Home will include a fridge, not the one currently in the kitchen. Backyard is full grass and awnings to provide nice shade while entertaining on the large patio. The flooring has all been replaced in the last few years as well as opening the dining area to the entire upstairs living space creating an inclusing entertaining area. The basement rec room has a wonderful entertaining space as well, including a wet bar to watch those games uninterupted. Have a sauna in your own home and keep that skin hydrated during our dry winter months and muscles loose after a great day of skiing. Tons of storage as well as quiet bedrooms for peaceful living. Don't wait for the open house to come for a private showing.
